Type: Package
Package: eemanalyzeR
Title: Semi-Automated Processing of Excitation Emission Matrices
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Katie A.", "Wampler", , "katie.wampler@oregonstate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5584-7554")),
    person("Ryan P.", "Cole", , "ryan.cole@oregonstate.edu", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Tools for processing and analyzing raw excitation-emission
    matrices (EEMs) and absorbance data.  Includes functions for data
    cleaning, quality assurance, calculation of indices, and generating
    visualizations.  Builds upon the 'eemR' and 'staRdom' packages to
    create a more streamlined and automated workflow that ensures
    consistent analysis and simplify the coding required to process the
    data.
License: AGPL (>= 3)
